---

## Micro-interactions

1. **Card expansion**: Smooth height animation (200ms ease-out)
2. **Scene scroll**: Snap to card edges
3. **Direction toggle**: Rotate chevron icon
4. **Button press**: Subtle scale (0.98) + haptic feedback
5. **Progress pills**: Gentle pulse when scene is edited

---

## Accessibility

- All cards reachable via keyboard/swipe
- Clear focus indicators
- Screen reader: "Scene 1 of 7, 10 seconds, Hey there..."
- Minimum touch target: 44Ã—44pt
- Sufficient color contrast (4.5:1 minimum)

---

## Visual Specs

| Element              | Value                    |
|----------------------|--------------------------|
| Card corner radius   | 12dp                     |
| Card padding         | 16dp                     |
| Card gap             | 8dp                      |
| Section label size   | 11sp, uppercase, 500wt   |
| Narration text       | 16sp, 400wt              |
| Direction text       | 14sp, 400wt, muted       |
| Duration badge       | 13sp, 500wt, pill shape  |
| Bottom CTA height    | 56dp                     |
| Safe area bottom     | 34dp (iOS) / 16dp (Android) |
